entities.description: Represents females aged 12-44 who are currently pregnant.
Indicates the pregnancy status of females aged 12-44, including unknown status, pregnant, not pregnant, or not applicable.
Indicates the current trimester of pregnancy for females aged 12-44.
Represents the body mass index (BMI) of the respondent, calculated based on weight and height.
Represents whether the respondent has talked to a doctor about virtual service treatment in the past year.

relationships.description: Relates the pregnant females aged 12-44 to their pregnancy status.
Relates the pregnancy status of females aged 12-44 to the current trimester of pregnancy.
Indicates the body mass index of the respondent.
Indicates whether the respondent has talked to a doctor about virtual service treatment in the past year.
